        <h2> Q2. Program to convert minutes to seconds </h2>

        <script>
            function minToSec(minutes){
                return Math.floor(minutes * 60);
            }
            var conversion = minToSec(100);
            console.log("Javascript converting minutes into seconds = " + conversion);            
        </script>

    </body>

</html> 
